round the\nprotostar regardless of the magnetic field strength, which may influence the\nfurther evolution of Population III stars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Aug 2013 04:53:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-16"}
