tou\\v{s}ek. Links to Bourgain--Milman--Wolfson type and a conjectural\nnonlinear Maurey--Pisier theorem are studied.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Aug 2013 13:13:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 19 Aug 2013 16:27:03 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 21 Oct 2013 16:21:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-10-22"}
